name: Erin Bradshaw
bio: World Champion Equestrian | Texas Born and Raised | Mom to Jessie Paxton Weiss | #JohnSimon

social_posts.post_text: First time meeting #Santa! She asked for a pony, I’m sure of it! 🎅🏻❤️
Had so much fun at my moms annual “Holiday Hat Luncheon!” #TisTheSeason 🎄
This city is absolutely magical at Christmas! 🎄
Last night was so special getting to see my dad inducted into the Sports Broadcaster Hall of Fame! We had an amazing time in New York celebrating him! 🖤

Jessie HOW are you one?! Thank you for making me a momma and giving me the best job in the world! Watching you grow over this last year has been one of the biggest blessings for your dad and I! You don’t meet a stranger and light up everyone you meet through your contagious and never ending smile! We had the best time celebrating YOU! Take good care of “Smalls” he is so lucky to have a little girl like you to love him and has a home for life with us! Now onto Christmas where we have to buy you more presents 🎁🤣 (what in the world do we get her now?!) We love you sweet thing!
It’s always a great day when you go to school and # “Bubbles” is there to greet you! Love this sweet girl and her little school! 🖤
Love my sisters! Merry Christmas y’all! 🎄🎁🎅🏻
Every now and then, we dress up! 🖤
Jessie loves her Eli! She is nothing but smiles when she’s on a horse! That’s my girl! She looks like a poodle 🐩 because her hair was in a top knot 🤣!
Happy Bachelorette to my big sis! So excited to spend the night celebrating YOU! 🖤
Celebrating the #bride to be! Happy Bridal Shower Day Sis! Love you!

Time to get @racheltbradshaw married! 

HAMU: @cherthalove 
Dress: @giannibiniofficial 
Shoes: @stevemadden 
Company: The Weiss’s 🤣
We had the most amazing weekend with our closest family and friends to celebrate @racheltbradshaw ! Love you sis, you looked stunning! 🤍
Excuse me while I go cry 😭! @scott_weiss12
Tonight @kt_cochran1 and I are #Swifties and you will never see me fan girl as hard as I’m about too!

Spring has sprung and it's time to get our yard looking its best thanks to @getsunday lawn products, which are now available in stores and online at @Loweshomeimprovement! Y’all know the damage the #Texas heat can do to your lawn 😆! 

I chose @getsunday products because they’re made with simple ingredients and have an easy hose on application…y'all know I love products that are simple and easy to use! Be sure and check them out at Lowes! #sundaypartner #sundayatlowes
Horse showin’ babe! 🖤

No better way to celebrate living in the greatest country ever yesterday than winning the Amateur Western Pleasure with ELICIOUS! Such a good boy!

❤️🤍💙

I am forever thankful for these two horses! They gave me their all this year at the World Show and that’s why they’re THE. Best. Boys! 🖤

JOHN SIMON - Reserve World Champion Senior Trail with Troy Lehn

ELICIOUS - World Champion Amateur Pleasure and Reserve Sweepstakes Champion Non Pro Maturity

Also please note Jessie 😂 she will for sure be taking both of them from me in the next two years, she loves them!
Swingin’ sticks in #Alaska! ⛳️
Gangs all here! 🎣
Welcome “Baby Girl!” Jessie. Is. Going. To. Die! And no her name is not Etta 🤣.
Thank you Afognak Youth Charity for having us out to your Golf Tournament! Such a great time in one of the most beautiful places! ⛳️ 🙌🏻😎
Pool babe 💙🤍🩵!
I love her love for animals! It’s amazing what animals can teach kids at such a young age…patience, love and respect. 🩵

Tomorrow we bury my beautiful and amazing Nannie. She was the matriarch of our family but I know she is where she wanted to be the most, with my PaPa in heaven! I hope I can be half the woman she was and I am so glad she got to meet Jessie!
Not ☝🏼 a cat person...this one showed up at our barn two weeks ago and the rest is history. Please note the pose with the cat…I cannnnnnnnnot ✋🏻!
So happy to celebrate our beautiful friends! Wishing you the best Morgan and FJ, we love y’all! 🖤
Had the best day at the @thedallasarboretum! What a stunning set up, if you have a chance to go, I highly recommend! 🎃🍂
There is a reason he is family. John Simon you are a SAINT! Jessie absolutely loves him 🖤.
It’s Fall and she is a vibe! 🖤🎃🧡🍂

Family photos were a success! I couldn’t choose just one…even if we had to get Baby Girl and a kitten to make it happen! Thank you @carleyandcophotography for once again capturing our family so perfectly! 🖤 #fallfamilyphotos
Today was so much fun! To get to spend Thanksgiving in this city with family and see the parade through Jessie’s eyes was a moment I’ll remember forever! Happy Thanksgiving y’all!
SANTA! “I know him!” 🎅🏻🎄
If you’re in #NewYork and get to see @danwhitemagic , I 10/10 recommend! My mind was blown, he was amazing! 🖤🪄

Happy SECOND Birthday sweet girl! We had the best weekend celebrating you! You are the light of our lives, and the absolute best thing that ever happened to us! You light up every room you walk into with your amazing personality, we love you so much! Thank you to everyone who came out to celebrate her this weekend!
Just an average ranchin’ babe with her best broodmare “Princess!”
World Champion Equestrian | Texas Born and Raised | Mom to Jessie Paxton Weiss | #JohnSimon
